Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.59,0:00:12.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:17.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.99,0:00:30.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:37.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:44.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:51.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.56,0:01:00.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:05.53,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.57,0:01:10.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.53,0:01:16.38,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.42,0:01:22.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.34,0:01:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了逃离企图夺取 『蔚蓝之水』的邪恶三人组
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不幸在海上漂流的强 娜蒂亚与大王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.48,0:01:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得到美国战舰的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是战舰却在 神秘大海兽的攻击下重创
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强他们也被迫 再度回到海上漂流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:49.63,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#04 万能潜水艇鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那两个孩子究竟是到哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森 我们要在这里待到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要等到晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚上藉由星星就能晓得位置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到时再到最近的岛屿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你打算穿那身装扮到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等到我能洗澡的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.96,0:02:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在下身为堂堂绅士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能因为炎热就穿着邋遢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我的原则
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你就快去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看了就烦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么我都遇不到好男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么我的运气会这么差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打起精神来吧 都不像你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是跟我在一起 才害你有这种下场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在死前我要先向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一点都不介意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟你在一起我觉得很快乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 我是在跟大王道歉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你肚子饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我马上抓条大鱼给你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 可是我不吃鱼喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是在对大王说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那头海兽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又折回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 它是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一动也不动的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 娜蒂亚呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是金属
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这家伙并不是海兽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是由人类制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两名遇难者已经收容完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来这就是海兽的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是潜水艇 潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,潜水艇？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以自由潜入海里的船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是个大发明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,击沉战舰与你爸爸的船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会不会就是这艘船？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那可不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是排水口吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你很开心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,搭完新型战舰之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又能搭到这么棒的潜水艇耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是太走运了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看 这并没有打铆钉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是怎么焊接的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是小孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长 右舷两点钟方向 出现微弱磁气反应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那家伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.97,0:06:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距离太过遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许是那艘战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不晓得 总之先接近再说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎启动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解 引擎启动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是引擎的声音 要启航了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两舷全速 路线变更027
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是要去哪里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这具引擎已经挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,磁气反应未出现改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相对速度目前约32节
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶的石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在死区虽然让你溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 我的运气似乎还很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长 请问要如何处置遇难者？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,副舰长 是你开口说要救人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那两个孩子似乎满坚强的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我讨厌小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您明明是讨厌所有的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 这艘船为什么要救我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我们被困在海上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许他们也跟那3个人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是为了想拿到『蔚蓝之水』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔚蓝之水！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样多疑不好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总比随便相信人好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然没有门把 但这个应该是门没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要拜托这艘船上的人 让我参观船舱内部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有没有人啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们不会伤害你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船可能是那只海中怪兽耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 连面都还没见过 说话这么失礼不好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对别人客气一点 这样对自己也比较好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那位公主名叫娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而我则是王子 名叫强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 谢谢你 强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的名字是艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 他人的好意 你就接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们可以参观船舱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且『蔚蓝之水』没有发光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就表示没有危险 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好窄又好奇怪的走廊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,硬梆梆又古怪的门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请问你就是艾丽朵拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧 你们先把湿衣服换下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的确 这个房间好凉快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:10:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是因为房里有冷气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冷气？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 夏天也能让房间 保持凉爽的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夏天还能这么凉爽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那可是人类最大的享受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那究竟是怎样的构造？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这点之后再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们先去冲个澡 换上干净的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冲澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是热可可亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好神奇的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是魔法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是 这是科学的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的确 这艘船根本就是科学的精华嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是哪个国家的船？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来不像是法国
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那会是英国 还是美国？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们不属于任何一个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是海盗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:10:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们是追捕海盗的那一方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那为什么要戴上那种面具？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要没看过我们的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算回到陆地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也没办法告诉他人 你们见过什么人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们是一群已经和陆地 断绝关系的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以希望你们能将 在这里见过的事全都忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你愿意让我们回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 我们目前正在追踪 重要的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没时间放你们下船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我一定会负起责任 将你们送回陆地上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长也把你们交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我记得『尼莫』在拉丁文里 代表着『什么人都不是』的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 你懂得真多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那并不是他的本名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但却是最适合船长的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那艾丽朵拉也不是你的本名吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就任凭你们想像了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我每天会送两次餐点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然少了点 但就先忍忍啰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见 你们要好好相处喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这颗『蔚蓝之水』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在我被卖到马戏团的时候 就带在身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说我身上就只有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个时候你几岁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不晓得…那时候我还很小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有『蔚蓝之水』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能成为我寻找家人的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,熄灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该是代表晚上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本不晓得 现在是白天还是晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就连这艘船要去哪里也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之 这应该是叫我们该睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你醒着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还是觉得这艘船不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是艾丽朵拉对我们很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以才不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会平白无故对别人好 一定另有企图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我…遇到的人都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 我想发明了 这么厉害潜水艇的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该不会是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们或许是害了你爸爸的人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并不一定是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要凡事都往不好的方面想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要先请他们 让我参观这艘船的机械设备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后再慢慢想以后的事就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我讨厌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:14:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我并没有讨厌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 前半部停机库的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如何？有办法修吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把引擎换掉也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 没错 就照你的意思改装
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请尽快 那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是到这里来之后吃的 第5顿玉米汤 面包及牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说已经3天了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要到什么时候才能出去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论按哪个键都打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被锁住了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么办？强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之 我想请他们 先让我参观船舱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们连脸都不肯让你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么可能会让你参观船舱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,风好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是艾丽朵拉说的冷气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是灯光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长 请立刻前来舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,掌握到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 舰首2点钟方向 发现引擎声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,捕捉到目标
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,方位32度 距离9200
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是石像鬼的潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,速度呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,约8节 正朝本舰航行中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是被发现了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该不会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主动声纳呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并未发出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要攻击吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 先按兵不动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次一定要找出 石像鬼的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,预定接触位置还有300秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距离呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接近至8800
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 在被对方声纳发现前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进行无声潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰停止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:16:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进行无声潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主引擎停止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船停下来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,水深固定于120
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,辅助引擎停止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两舷平衡一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自动悬吊 切换完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,速度3节
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,消磁装置 开始运作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰启动防爆鱼雷防御
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰启动防爆鱼雷防御
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,防水闸门封闭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所有水密舱门固定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,固定结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,防爆准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,熄灯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙的情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 距离7500
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,方位及速度不变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是推进器遭战舰破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是陷阱？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距离接近至7000
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距离接近至5000
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距离3000
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绝对不能发出声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该不会是那两个孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被发现了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,速度 方位皆不变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,未发出主动声纳 距离1200
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以肉眼确认目标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即将通过本舰上方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有东西正从上面经过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,深水炸弹 从正上方过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎全开 垂直上升
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,受损情况呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第1辅助引擎中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰首右舷中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进水极轻微
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从7时至7时5分方向 逐渐远离
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距离800 速度12节
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别让它跑了 左舷回转160度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,侦测到鱼雷发射声 4枚 距离1200
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全速回避
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鱼雷防御
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,受损情形呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,未遭击中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并无进水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,压载一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拉回水平位置
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,敌舰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找不到 声波混乱无法辨识
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,航海仪器及电罗经也全部失常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船身周围遭强力磁场覆盖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鱼雷之中似乎含有妨碍物质
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在移动会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰停止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.98,0:21:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被摆了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又得重头来过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.31,0:22:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两个人都出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,外头 该说再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.15,0:22:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好久没见到太阳了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.99,0:22:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 我还是没能参观到船舱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒 变成水上飞机了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.44,0:22:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是鹦鹉螺号和我所送的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 万能潜水艇鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从这里往南飞会有座大岛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.99,0:22:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那里有船开往法国
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还在飞机里放了罗盘 地图 以及一点食物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.56,0:22:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:22:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长给的时间 只剩下5分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 你还在做什么 快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你的帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 保重了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.24,0:23:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见了 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.31,0:23:54.15,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.22,0:24:02.32,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.39,0:24:07.39,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.46,0:24:11.83,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.90,0:24:20.78,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.84,0:24:30.88,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.95,0:24:39.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.70,0:24:43.93,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.00,0:24:48.56,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.64,0:24:58.01,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.39,0:25:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,离开鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.13,0:25:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,载着我们两个人 与一只动物的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.59,0:25:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然遭到攻击而坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.56,0:25:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原本和平的岛屿 遭到侵略者占领
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.40,0:25:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,化为一座恐怖之岛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.27,0:25:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 这孩子还活着 她还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.87,0:25:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉…振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.88,0:25:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『玛莉之岛』
